    "7227502": {
        "Desc": "Complete the challenge",
        "Tips": "Go to Quest Menu to access Quest Hints",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "Ah, you have been recognized by all the Jibashiri. They represent the will of Watatsumi, and so have you obtained the right to learn everything."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "You are the savior of the people of Watatsumi, and are one acknowledged by Watatsumi also. Thus, you have earned the right to ask and to be answered."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "Still, I ask that you follow the rules and not take the truth beyond this ocean abyss."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "What else do you wish to know?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Tell me about the Bathysmal Vishaps..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "They are primordial elemental beings, unbent and unbowed by the power that came from the heavens owing to their living deep underwater."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "They are actually very intelligent, and they are adept at evolving. They would even evolve into different elemental forms throughout the history of their war against us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "I would not be surprised at all if they have learned language or perhaps even evolved into lizard-people of a sort."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "The Holy Soil phenomenon is, in fact, the expansion of their habitat. That means that the primordial elemental power of the three realms is growing stronger."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "Only by using Watatsumi Omikami's life force to awaken its second servant could we convert this raw, raging elemental power."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Tell me about Watatsumi Omikami..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "Watatsumi Omikami, due to ill-fortune, fell into this place, beyond the jurisdiction of the heavenly order."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "This was undoubtedly to the good fortune of us, the people of Byakuyakoku. It has done a great many things for us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "Unfortunately, by making contact with us, it also grasped a truth that came before its own existence. Thus, it was forced by heaven to sacrifice itself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "The truth behind this sacrifice had to remain unknown to all. Only thus could the people of Byakuyakoku be allowed to live under the rule of The Seven."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So, what were things like before the sun and moon?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "Before Byakuyakoku fell into the deep sea, the whole world had a single unified culture."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "Later, a great war broke out, in which the heavens capsized and the earth was ripped asunder. This land was then plunged into the dark ocean depths."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "However, the heavenly order seemed to not wish for those who remembered all this to remain on the earth. We searched and searched for a road of return, but there was none to be found."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "Much, much later, heaven's powers of prohibition would gradually weaken. Thus did Watatsumi Omikami manage to fall into this place."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Tell me about the Dainichi Mikoshi."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "The Dainichi Mikoshi was constructed by the Sage Abrax. It has the power to bring light to the dark depths."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "It has quite a few other functions, to boot."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "All in all, it is a very powerful device."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I've got nothing else to ask."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eboshi",
                    "T": "Fair enough. Again, please remember to keep all that you have seen here in Enkanomiya an eternal secret."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
